flowchart LR
  A[Ideate<br/>hypotheses + domain input]
  B[Prototype<br/>EDA + quick transforms]
  C[Validate<br/>leakage + coverage + stability]
  D[Materialize<br/>batch/stream/on-demand]
  E[Register<br/>metadata + ownership + version]
  F[Serve<br/>offline PIT + online low-latency]
  G[Monitor<br/>freshness + drift + nulls]

  A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F --> G
  G -->|new data / decay| A

